Package: blackbox-framework
Version: 2.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: python2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/jothatron/blackbox
Description: A Python-based network analysis and exploitation toolkit
 Blackbox is a modular security tool for network scanning, exploitation,
 and post-exploitation. It requires Python 2 and supports multiple attack vectors.
